<view class="page">
  <view class="card">
    <view class="title">力量数据（卧推 / 硬拉 / 深蹲）</view>
    <view class="hint">
      你可以直接填 1RM；或填一个重量与对应次数来估算 1RM。注意：估算更适合“接近力竭”的那一组（top set）。
    </view>

    <view class="section">
      <view class="section-title">卧推</view>
      <view class="row">
        <view class="item">
          <view class="label">直接 1RM（kg）</view>
          <input class="input" type="number" placeholder="可不填" value="{{form.bench.direct1rm}}" data-field="bench.direct1rm" bindinput="onInput" />
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="row">
        <view class="item">
          <view class="label">重量（kg）</view>
          <input class="input" type="number" placeholder="如 80" value="{{form.bench.weight}}" data-field="bench.weight" bindinput="onInput" />
        </view>
        <view class="item">
          <view class="label">次数</view>
          <input class="input" type="number" placeholder="如 8" value="{{form.bench.reps}}" data-field="bench.reps" bindinput="onInput" />
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="preview">估算 1RM：{{preview.bench1rm || '-'}}</view>
    </view>

    <view class="section">
      <view class="section-title">硬拉</view>
      <view class="row">
        <view class="item">
          <view class="label">直接 1RM（kg）</view>
          <input class="input" type="number" placeholder="可不填" value="{{form.deadlift.direct1rm}}" data-field="deadlift.direct1rm" bindinput="onInput" />
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="row">
        <view class="item">
          <view class="label">重量（kg）</view>
          <input class="input" type="number" placeholder="如 140" value="{{form.deadlift.weight}}" data-field="deadlift.weight" bindinput="onInput" />
        </view>
        <view class="item">
          <view class="label">次数</view>
          <input class="input" type="number" placeholder="如 5" value="{{form.deadlift.reps}}" data-field="deadlift.reps" bindinput="onInput" />
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="preview">估算 1RM：{{preview.deadlift1rm || '-'}}</view>
    </view>

    <view class="section">
      <view class="section-title">深蹲</view>
      <view class="row">
        <view class="item">
          <view class="label">直接 1RM（kg）</view>
          <input class="input" type="number" placeholder="可不填" value="{{form.squat.direct1rm}}" data-field="squat.direct1rm" bindinput="onInput" />
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="row">
        <view class="item">
          <view class="label">重量（kg）</view>
          <input class="input" type="number" placeholder="如 120" value="{{form.squat.weight}}" data-field="squat.weight" bindinput="onInput" />
        </view>
        <view class="item">
          <view class="label">次数</view>
          <input class="input" type="number" placeholder="如 6" value="{{form.squat.reps}}" data-field="squat.reps" bindinput="onInput" />
        </view>
      </view>
      <view class="preview">估算 1RM：{{preview.squat1rm || '-'}}</view>
    </view>

    <view class="btn-row">
      <button class="btn btn-outline" bindtap="onSaveLocal">保存到本地</button>
      <button class="btn btn-primary" bindtap="onUpload">上传/更新力量</button>
    </view>
  </view>
</view>

